<collectingCountry box="[427,571,476,501]" name="South Africa" pageId="13">South Africa</collectingCountry>
(Fig. 4).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="13.[151,1437,151,680]" box="[199,542,511,536]" pageId="13">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,417,511,536]" pageId="13">Floral association.</emphasis>
Unknown.
</paragraph>
